@DATABASE "Atom Ant"
@NODE "MAIN" "SPECCY POKES - A - Atom Ant"
@TOC "MAIN"

                   ZX SPECTRUM (SPECCY heheh) POKES - A
                   ====================================

                                 Atom Ant
                                 ========


DESCRIPTION              POKE
===========              ====
            
@{"Infinite Lives" RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(49384,0) zxampoke(49444,0)"}          49384,0:49444,0
@{"Immunity      " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(49374,24) zxampoke(49435,24)"}          49374,24:49435,24


                         For various reasons (like decrunching and stuff),
                         you have to activate the POKEs once you start to
                         PLAY the game. this was the easiest approach for
                         multiface POKEs, as otherwise there would be
                         about 30 POKEs to put in, which while OK for
                         DATA statements, is a pain in the butt to do
                         POKE by POKE).

                         This is one of my POKEs. Enjoy!

                         Rastan.
@endnode
